{"tid":1089713,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"Westbrook CLS","createTime":"2019-04-03T03:38:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-03T15:48:29.000Z","uid":18254,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6d4011170599e4dd2024ec561181b6a1a7ecd107","tid":1089713,"uid":18254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T03:38:14.000Z","msg":"Westbrook創造瘋狂之夜！繼承神獸紀錄的忍者龜。<br />\n🏀單場達到20分20籃板20助攻門檻<br />\n🏀51年來的第一人<br />\n<br />\n-<br />\n<br />\n今晚的Russell Westbrook沒有極限，與湖人之戰全場貢獻20分20籃板21助攻外帶3抄截，這令他成為NBA歷史時隔51年後，又一位超級巨星能夠單場寫下『三個20+』的怪物表現，而上一位就是『上古神獸』Wilt Chamberlain，他在51年前曾拿下22分25籃板與21助攻的驚人演出。<br />\n<br />\n-<br />\n<br />\n我一直在講Westbrook不是一個完美的球員，但他絕對是在場上最拚最燃燒小宇宙的一名戰士，擁有能量最強、鬥志最悍、最不討喜的敵人標籤。<br />\n<br />\n今天與湖人第一節的比賽，Westbrook就運籌帷幄替隊友傳出許多好球，也替雷霆率先開出優勢，不得不說，Westbrook他的全面性對於球隊真的太重要。<br />\n<br />\n-<br />\n<br />\n且恐怖的是，Westbrook即將要連續三個賽季『平均大三元』，默默地，這賽季他也寫下了31場大三元表現，然而這已經讓球迷習以為常，這就是最驚人的地方。<br />\n<br />\n雖然本季大三元帶來的團隊勝率沒有過去兩年高，但31場比賽裡替球隊拿下21勝10敗也是相當出色的成績，代表Westbrook越全能發揮，雷霆贏面就是水漲船高。"},{"pid":"2481daa7ac5962db6555648c227364f86098aae9","tid":1089713,"uid":54359,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T03:43:13.000Z","msg":"3樣數據都岩岩好20，係助攻多1個<br />\n擺明刷數據<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5479fd4e6fa27eae9d871064327453fb590f48ef","tid":1089713,"uid":241930,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"2481daa7ac5962db6555648c227364f86098aae9","tid":1089713,"uid":54359,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T03:43:13.000Z","msg":"3樣數據都岩岩好20，係助攻多1個<br />\n擺明刷數據<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T04:09:20.000Z","msg":"最尾嗰個rebound都係嘅. 但係真係唔係個個想做就做到.<br />\n<br />\n所以吹佢唔漲"},{"pid":"b25f6fa0ccb91709a08a39105c719380fb575095","tid":1089713,"uid":217336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T04:13:13.000Z","msg":"一個控衛搶到5個進攻板算係勁喇，多過人全隊"},{"pid":"c6ac68c174f06f52af7957c3e101796f7ce32eba","tid":1089713,"uid":18254,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"b25f6fa0ccb91709a08a39105c719380fb575095","tid":1089713,"uid":217336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T04:13:13.000Z","msg":"一個控衛搶到5個進攻板算係勁喇，多過人全隊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T07:13:29.000Z","msg":"一個後衛20個籃板或者20個助攻都難啦，更何況20個籃板+20個助攻"},{"pid":"c72778ca1f5c819745dd28c7a28014ace893d998","tid":1089713,"uid":144427,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T08:32:37.000Z","msg":"好中意雷霆 因為佢帶領成隊都打得好有火"},{"pid":"6571dca92e43306a05f49fb83bece21dec7acd5a","tid":1089713,"uid":106675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T08:33:55.000Z","msg":"然後playoff 1st round exit<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80a5066451c77e7573d8b26049e2bbc662132a9f","tid":1089713,"uid":70988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6571dca92e43306a05f49fb83bece21dec7acd5a","tid":1089713,"uid":106675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T08:33:55.000Z","msg":"然後playoff 1st round exit<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T10:44:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42e3faaac9230ed6284ba8e596c77dd68b6b6b67","tid":1089713,"uid":53855,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T10:51:14.000Z","msg":"好撚勁，搶五個進攻板，體能唔野小"},{"pid":"f38f4bdb0e5c2d0fec1f0e8e7069fabb6722f22c","tid":1089713,"uid":10014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T11:00:11.000Z","msg":"KD肯留低，佢地兩個可唔可以帶到雷有勇咁既高度？"},{"pid":"2f7e055609f921a0c99ebf